        "text": "This paper analyses and addresses the problem of data sparsity and long-tailed distribution in RQ-SID by identifying data sparsity and long-tailed distribution as the primary causes, and proposes effective solutions to mitigate this issue, thereby significantly enhancing the effectiveness of generative retrieval in real-world E-commerce applications."
